casebody.data:
David B. Harrell, plaintiff in error, vs. Robert J. Grimes, defendant in error. Hawkins & Burke, by R. H. Clark, for plaintiff in error. E. H. Beall, J. L. Wimberly, by A. Hood, for defendant.

The bill of exceptions in this caase was dismissed because it was not served till the eleventh day after it was certified by the Judge below. (E.)
